<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.2">
<l>alliyampū malarkkōtā yaṭipaṇintēṉ viṇṇappam</l>
<l>collukēṉkēṭ ṭaruḷāytu ṇaimalarkkaṇ maṭamāṉē</l>
<l>yelliyampō tiṉitirutta liruntatōri ṭavakaiyil</l>
<l>mallikaimā mālaikoṇṭaṅ kārttatumō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady with a lovely water-lily flower blossom garland!</l>
<l rend="indent">I bow at [your] feet. Salutations!</l>
<l>Graciously hear me speak,</l>
<l rend="indent">you gentle doe with a pair of blossom eyes!</l>
<l>Sweetly waiting patiently in a solitary place at dusk,</l>
<l>[and] binding [Him] there with an auspicious garland of jasmine.</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
